scopecontent.p:
Divided into three subseries: Coquette,
                  1926-1933;
                  Emily Bridgers Estate, 1924-1944; and Miscellany, 1913-1959, and undated.
                  Includes legal matters relating to the play Coquette; the will and estate of Miss Bridgers' aunt, Emily Bridgers;
                  receipts and furniture inventories; and other miscellaneous items. Arranged
                  chronologically within each subseries.
